--- Soundwave ---

Soundwave picks up the cassettes and inserts them into his 
cassette slot. He turns to the council, and nods his approval, "I am 
ready to depart, is there anything else you would like me to do?" 
He laughs in his mind at Havotron's bumbling ally, <This should be 
interesting, if Havotron's bots are this stupid all the time, I might 
have to take over and run the show myself.> Again, he smiles 
inwardly, and chuckles.
